messages.messageBody:
Hey everyone-
Well, this is it. I am down to 7 days and counting. My home is torn up and packed down (and pushed into boxes, LOL) The necessities are still out, refrigerator, stove, computer, stereo, husband, children, pets...:) I am officially no mail/ web until the move is complete. I will check in on the egroups site, to keep current. I hope that everyone has a great May, and partial June. You can reach me via private email over the next few weeks, I will still be checking the mail. I just will not have very much time. Sorry about the crossposting:)
Blessings and prayers
Stephanie
